snippet.textDisplay:
My interpretation of the video: There are three guys, one lead singer Maanu, other antogonist who is scheming to break them up, but pretending to be their friend. He makes Maanu think lead singer Annural is being unfaithful to him with 3rd guy who we also see leaveing her room at start, but in actual might not know how it and how it looked, i.e. be there wrong time wrong place situation and may only be a colleague/friend. Antagonist uses that, even puts scarf Maanu gave to girl in 3rd guys room, we can see his pic next to chair from where Maanu finds scarf thinking she gave to him (beside it having emotional value), in actual she left it on her seat when taking stage to sing. Another female who maybe her friend and observes it, and tells Annural same, who goes after him, but she is too late. I guess thus kind of 70s era in video otherwise u can always call ;)
Great video, beautiful music. Maanu is always good, while Annural definitely stole hearts in this song, and ofcourse also that flute playing by Dawood, like in most songs this season is brilliant.
